{"tid":1576548,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"612 被催淚彈擊中頭受傷　港台司機入禀向警務處處長索償","createTime":"2019-09-17T09:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T11:13:28.000Z","uid":68738,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"94ca3565f8eaf04df4fb7c3b2fd91ca1624be6bf","tid":1576548,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202019-09-1720at205.36.4820PM_BH2cG_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202019-09-1720at205.36.4820PM_BH2cG_1200x0.png&h=6be5af50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6.12 警民衝突期間，警方發射超過 150 枚催淚彈清場。當日被催淚彈擊中頭部暈倒的《香港電台》外判司機莊文龍，今日入禀區域法院，就其人身傷害向警務處處長索償。<br />\n<br />\n原告人為莊文龍，被告則由律政司代表警務處處長盧偉聰。入禀狀指，莊文龍當時站在中信大廈外一段龍匯道的行人路上，被一枚催淚彈擊中頭部暈倒，當時他身穿反光背心以顯示他是一名新聞工作者。<br />\n<br />\n入禀狀要求警務處處長就警隊所作的襲擊、酷刑、疏忽，或違反法例或人權的做法，而對莊文龍造成的人身傷害作賠償。<br />\n<br />\n莊文龍當日運送器材時，於行人路上被催淚彈擊中受傷。港台報道，他事隔一個月身體仍有後遺症，全身多處皮膚敏感、流膿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/612-%E8%A2%AB%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%93%8A%E4%B8%AD%E9%A0%AD%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%85%A5%E7%A6%80%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F612-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%2593%258A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A6%2580%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F%2F&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2FzkC3bY0i4P88JjHF8GLL0M%3D&h=912f03ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F612-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%2593%258A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%